[http://www.ruckuswireless.com/products/zoneflex-indoor/7962 Product page] The '''Ruckus Wireless''' logo and "Giterdone 9" is silkscreened on the non-component side of the board. :"FAB 100-11120-001 REV 5" is on the component side of the main board. The '''Ruckus Wireless''' logo, "PATENTS PENDING", "Redshift", and "FAB 100-11122-001 REV 5" is silkscreened on the main antenna board. Per the FCC manual, the default SSIDs are '''Wireless1''' through '''Wireless4'''.
